          "type": "buttongroup",
          "options": [
            { "value": "cust-123", "label": "Acme Corp (New York)" },
            { "value": "cust-456", "label": "Acme Industries (Texas)" },
            { "value": "none", "label": "Neither - search again" }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  }
}
```
